elements.name: Deseo ingresar a la aplicación, ver la lista de miembros, crear un miembro, volver al listado y crear un miembro con el mismo email para validar que no se permite su creaciòn

steps.name: I go to "<GHOST-VERSION-2-URL1>"
I wait for 2 seconds
I enter email "<USERNAME>" into selector "input[name='identification']"
I enter password "<PASSWORD>" into selector "input[name='password']"
I take screenshot of step "1" and scenario "<ESCENARIO_4>" and feature "Miembros" and version "<GHOST-VERSION-2>"
I push login button with selector "button[type='submit']"
I wait for 5 seconds
I expect to enter to Ghost home page "<GHOST-VERSION-2-URL2>"
I click on member list with selector "a[href='#/members/']"
I take screenshot of step "2" and scenario "<ESCENARIO_4>" and feature "Miembros" and version "<GHOST-VERSION-2>"
I expect to enter to Ghost Members section "<GHOST-VERSION-2-URL3>"
I wait for 1 seconds
I click on New Member with selector "a[href='#/members/new/']"
I wait for 1 seconds
I enter member Name "$name_4" into selector "input[name='name']"
I enter member email "$$name_4" from provider "@hotmail.com" into selector "input[name='email']"
I enter member note "frankcandanoza@hotmail.com" into selector "textarea[name='note']"
I take screenshot of step "3" and scenario "<ESCENARIO_4>" and feature "Miembros" and version "<GHOST-VERSION-2>"
I push Save member button with selector "button[class='gh-btn gh-btn-primary gh-btn-icon ember-view']"
I wait for 1 seconds
I go to Ghost Members section "<GHOST-VERSION-2-URL3>"
I take screenshot of step "4" and scenario "<ESCENARIO_4>" and feature "Miembros" and version "<GHOST-VERSION-2>"
I wait for 2 seconds
I click on New Member with selector "a[href='#/members/new/']"
I wait for 1 seconds
I enter member Name "$$name_1" into selector "input[name='name']"
I enter member email "$$name_4" from provider "@hotmail.com" into selector "input[name='email']"
I enter member note "frankcandanoza@hotmail.com" into selector "textarea[name='note']"
I take screenshot of step "5" and scenario "<ESCENARIO_4>" and feature "Miembros" and version "<GHOST-VERSION-2>"
I push Save member button with selector "button[class='gh-btn gh-btn-primary gh-btn-icon ember-view']"
I wait for 2 seconds
I take screenshot of step "6" and scenario "<ESCENARIO_4>" and feature "Miembros" and version "<GHOST-VERSION-2>"
